<div id="pf4448" class="pf w4e h303" data-page-no="4448"><div class="pc pc4448 w4e h303"><div class="t m117f xb7 h5 y2ef0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 4 July 22 28 </div><div class="t md0e x0 h1f9 y2bb1 ff1 fs58 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Revival and </div><div class="t m5f9 x0 h1f9 y239c ff1 fs58 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Reformation </div><div class="t m715 x11 h5 y51e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Blow ye the trumpet in Zion, and </div><div class="t m37d x3 h5 y2af ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sound an alarm in my holy mountain: </div><div class="t m720 x3 h5 y7a6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">let all the inhabitants of the land </div><div class="t m9c0 x3 h5 y4fa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tremble: for the day of the Lord </div><div class="t m602 x3 h5 ybec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cometh, foi it is nigh at hand&quot; (Joel </div><div class="t m5a3 x3 h5 y7ec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2:1). </div><div class="t m620 x11 h35 yaaa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The prophet wrote these words </div><div class="t mf1d x3 h35 ye62 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">under divine inspiration as a timely </div><div class="t m1471 x3 h35 y8ee ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">admonition when Israel was about to </div><div class="t m9fa xbd h35 y39e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be invaded by an enemy people. This </div><div class="t m978 x3 h35 ya73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is the immediate historical </div><div class="t m9ce xbd h35 y569 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">application. But these words were </div><div class="t m9cd xbd h35 y18f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preserved because they refer also to </div><div class="t m3c5 xbd h35 y363 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the time of the end, to the final &quot;day of </div><div class="t m744 xbd h35 y7b0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Lord,&quot; the eve of the second </div><div class="t m6e2 xbd h35 y666 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coming of Christ. The prophet calls for </div><div class="t m3ec xbd h35 yf7d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a trumpet to be sounded in Zion </div><div class="t m433 xbd h35 y405 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Jerusalem), representative of the </div><div class="t m5e3 xbd h35 y159f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church. The message was to spread an </div><div class="t m198 xbd h35 y525 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">alarm in the holy mountain of God, </div><div class="t meab xbd h35 y120d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">namely, His church. </div><div class="t m39d x11 h35 y59f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;In view of that great day [the day of </div><div class="t m210 xbd h35 y3a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Lord] the word of God, in the most </div><div class="t m602 xbd h35 y3db ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">solemn and impressive language, calls </div><div class="t me61 xbd h35 y40a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon His people to arouse from their </div><div class="t mcd1 xbd h35 y11d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual lethargy and to seek His face </div><div class="t m13a6 xbd h35 y40c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with repentance and humiliation... . </div><div class="t mfd x17 h35 y2ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;To prepare a people to stand in the </div><div class="t m7c0 xbd h35 y66e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">day of God, a great work of reform was </div><div class="t m745 xbd h35 ye8c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to be accomplished. God saw that </div><div class="t me8b xbd h35 y1750 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many of His professed people were </div><div class="t m1117 xbd h35 yb87 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not building for eternity, and in His </div><div class="t m1b9 xbd h35 y171c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mercy He was about to send a message </div><div class="t m9fb x4 h35 yafc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of warning to arouse them from their </div><div class="t m12d x4 h35 y8f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stupor and lead them to make ready </div><div class="t m58e x4 h35 y5aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the coming of the Lord.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m7fd xbd h35 ya6d ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m16d x51 h35 ya6d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 311. </div><div class="t m85d x17 h35 y463 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In view of the earth-shaking events </div><div class="t mdd4 x4 h35 y913 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that are about to occur in &quot;the day of </div><div class="t m534 x4 h35 y1c3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Lord,&quot; church members must be </div><div class="t m47e x4 h35 y8dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">awakened by a voice of alarm. They </div><div class="t m286 x4 h35 y27c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must seek a deep and genuine  </div><div class="t m14d x1c h35 y1202 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">conversion. A spiritual reformation </div><div class="t m534 x1c h35 y2af ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must be effected in the church in </div><div class="t m740 x1c h35 y7a6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preparation for the great events of the </div><div class="t ma09 x1c h35 ydad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time of the end. </div><div class="t me97 x56 h35 y4a5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Undoubtedly we are living in the </div><div class="t m139 x1c h35 y778 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">supreme hour of history. God is ready </div><div class="t ma23 x1c h35 y100f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to intervene powerfully in the affairs of </div><div class="t m8af x1c h35 yaaa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this world. His work has to be finished </div><div class="t ma8b x1c h35 y53c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on earth. And before that, the Holy </div><div class="t m3c3 x5a h35 y378 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit is going to be poured out in His </div><div class="t m29d x1c h35 y39e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">greatest fullness in the showers of the </div><div class="t m655 x5a h35 y1814 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">latter rain. </div><div class="t m485 x56 h35 y569 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But as a preparation for all these </div><div class="t mb73 x1c h35 y18f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">outstanding events, the church of </div><div class="t m6cc x5a h35 y363 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God—and its individual </div><div class="t m9e5 x5a h35 y522 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">components—needs to pass through a </div><div class="t m1317 x5a h35 y496 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">deep revival and a complete </div><div class="t m30d x5a h35 yf7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reformation: a turning to God and a </div><div class="t m9a9 x5a h35 y405 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">change of life. Therefore, the call to a </div><div class="t m6d2 x5a h35 y159f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">genuine conversion must resound </div><div class="t m1316 x5a h35 y450 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">throughout Zion. </div><div class="t m174 x7 h35 y782 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We plan to study in this lesson the </div><div class="t m851 x5a h35 y59f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need for reformation, the signs of true </div><div class="t m2c8 x5a h35 y3a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reformation, the elements of </div><div class="t m6bd x5a h35 y3db ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reformation, the methods to </div><div class="t m33c x5a h35 ybd9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accomplish reformation, as well as the </div><div class="t m52f x5a h35 y11d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">efforts of the devil to counteract this </div><div class="t m3e2 x5a h35 yaf8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by a counterfeit. </div><div class="t m558 x5a h5 y66e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x5a h5 ye8c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m9e x4b h5 ye8c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Need of Revival and Reformation </div><div class="t m390 x4b h5 y1750 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Joel 2:12, 13) </div><div class="t m558 x5a h5 yb1f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m34a x4b h5 yb1f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Discovering Satanic Counterfeits </div><div class="t m112a x4b h5 y171c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 8:44) </div><div class="t mb7 x5a h5 y79d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m7a8 x4b h5 yafc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">New Light </div><div class="t mdc9 x4b h5 y8f2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 8:20) </div><div class="t m1ce xb0 h5 y5aa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mad2 x4b h5 y5aa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Signs of True Reformation </div><div class="t m648 x4b h5 y11f8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 7:15, 16) </div><div class="t m8a8 xb0 h5 y463 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m60e x4b h5 y463 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Some Elements of Reformation </div><div class="t mdd5 x4b h5 y913 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eph. 4:22-24) </div><div class="t m2ef xb0 h5 y107b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t ma6c x4b h5 y7c5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How to Accomplish Revival and </div><div class="t ma46 x4b h5 y8dd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Reformation </div><div class="t m74f x4b h5 ya36 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 12:2) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
